(1, 2, '2017-11-16 14:47:09', '2017-11-16 14:47:09', '<h2>Here\'s a great way to support families affected by cancer!</h2>\r\nOne of the best ways to help us in our mission is to host an event for Tony Foundation. Events are fun, exciting ways to bring people together for a great cause! Also, hosting Tony Foundation events increases community exposure for your business, fosters networking, and showcases your group or organization\'s commitment to charity.\r\n\r\nBig or small, every fundraiser helps us meet our goal of helping families affected by cancer.\r\n\r\nDo you have an existing event that you would like to benefit Tony Foundation? Have a great idea for a new event? Interested in discussing fundraiser opportunities? If so, we\'d love to hear from you! Please <a href=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/contact\">contact us</a>.', 'Host an Event', 'One of the best ways to help us in our mission is to host an event for Tony Foundation. Big or small, every fundraiser helps us meet our goal of assisting families affected by cancer ...', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'host-an-event', '', '', '2018-04-04 18:18:30', '2018-04-04 18:18:30', '', 0, 'http://wpengine.com9/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
