(99, 3, '2018-03-07 03:16:53', '2018-03-07 03:16:53', 'Tony worked in Sales with Henry Schein Medical when he was forced out of work by a second cancer diagnosis. He previously worked in the solid waste and recycling industry, as well as being a sales manager for Rebath of Austin. He graduated from St. Edward\'s University in Austin with a degree in Broadcast Journalism. He is married to Carrie Laudadio, and a father to 3 daughters- Sierra, Gemma, and Alex.', 'Tony Laudadio', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tony-laudadio', '', '', '2018-04-20 21:53:44', '2018-04-20 21:53:44', '', 0, 'http://tonyfoundation.wpengine.com?post_type=tfpeople&#038;p=99', 0, 'tfpeople', '', 0),
