(253, 2, '2018-05-01 22:56:25', '2018-05-01 22:56:25', 'The response to our launch has been amazing. We can\'t say thanks enough to those of you who have reached out, expressed support, donated to our cause or just passed along our website and other info to your friends and colleagues.\r\n\r\nWe\'re excited to have our first big fundraiser on the calendar:\r\n\r\n<strong>Drive Away Cancer Golf Tournament: 9/28/2018</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Inaugural Tony Foundation Scramble Golf Tournament will be held at historic Lions Municipal Golf Course in Austin, Texas, on Friday, September 28, 2018. Please <a href=\"https://www.betterunite.com/tonyfoundation-driveawaycancergolftournament\">register today</a> to support the Tony Foundation and join us for a great day on the course. #DriveAwayCancer\r\n\r\n<strong>Connect with us today</strong>\r\n\r\nWe can’t do this without you! Over the coming weeks and months we will be announcing more fundraisers and other cool ways to contribute. There are a few things you can do right away to help:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Stay tuned by signing up for <a href=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/subscribe\">email updates,</a> liking our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tonyfoundation\">Facebook page,</a> and following us on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tonyfoundation/\">Instagram,</a> <a href=\"https://www.twitter.com/tony_foundation\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/27192820\">LinkedIn.</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Share Tony Foundation – send your friends and colleagues our website link (<a href=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/subscribe\">TonyFoundation.org</a>).</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/donate\">Donate,</a> if you are able. Large or small, every donation brings us closer to helping families in need.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith you on our team, we can truly make a difference in the lives of people who need our help.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Drive Away Cancer golf event set for September, and our thanks for your support', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'drive-away-cancer-golf-event-set-for-september-and-our-thanks-for-your-support', '', '', '2018-05-04 16:50:25', '2018-05-04 16:50:25', '', 0, 'http://tonyfoundation.org/?p=253', 0, 'post', '', 0),
