(275, 2, '2018-06-21 21:05:02', '2018-06-21 21:05:02', '[embed]https://youtu.be/p8CcKlwJF90[/embed]\r\n\r\nSpots are filling up fast for our Inaugural Tony Foundation Scramble Golf Tournament in Austin -- don\'t miss out on our special early bird pricing! Register by July 1 to take advantage of this special offer and help us <a href=\"https://www.betterunite.com/tonyfoundation-driveawaycancergolftournament\">Drive Away Cancer.</a>\r\n\r\nThe tournament will be a 9am shotgun start at historic Lions Golf Course on 9/28/18 for a great cause!\r\n\r\nYou can create your own group (foursome) or enter as an individual and we can get you hooked up with a good group. It will be a 4 person scramble format, BBQ will be served after the round, $5 mulligans can be purchased, and sponsorship opportunities are available.\r\n\r\nAll proceeds benefit Tony Foundation, helping to meet immediate needs for families whose primary income earners are impacted by cancer.\r\n\r\n<em>Special thanks to Brian Dickman for editing and producing our video!</em>', 'Drive Away Cancer Golf Tourney: Early Bird Rate Ends July 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'drive-away-cancer-golf-tourney-early-bird-rate-ends-july-1', '', '', '2018-06-21 23:58:59', '2018-06-21 23:58:59', '', 0, 'http://tonyfoundation.org/?p=275', 0, 'post', '', 0),
