(278, 2, '2018-08-14 23:53:02', '2018-08-14 23:53:02', 'Thanks to everyone for your support of our inaugural Drive Away Cancer Golf Tournament! We are excited to say that golfer registration is now SOLD OUT! We will have a full course of golfers at Lions on Sept. 28, which is great news.\r\n\r\nWe also have lots of sponsors signed up, but we are looking for more hole sponsors (businesses or individuals). Please visit our <a href=\"https://www.betterunite.com/tonyfoundation-driveawaycancergolftournament\">event page</a> or <a href=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/contact/\">contact us</a> if you\'re interested, or know someone who is.\r\n\r\nWe can\'t wait to see all 32 teams out at beautiful Lions Golf Course in September!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.betterunite.com/tonyfoundation-driveawaycancergolftournament\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-280\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Tony-at-Lions-300x253.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"253\" /></a>', 'Drive Away Cancer - Registrations Are Full!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'drive-away-cancer-registrations-are-full', '', '', '2018-08-15 01:35:22', '2018-08-15 01:35:22', '', 0, 'http://tonyfoundation.org/?p=278', 0, 'post', '', 0),
