(296, 2, '2018-09-13 00:57:21', '2018-09-13 00:57:21', 'When you become a recurring monthly donor to Tony Foundation, you\'re helping sustain us as we grow to meet our mission to assist as many families affected by cancer as possible. As a sign of our gratitude for your support, we offer the following thank you gifts for you to choose from.\r\n\r\n<strong>Helpers (Tier 1):</strong> For your $5 monthly recurring donation, please select your gift from the following items - TF Pen, TF Koozie, TF Cup 16oz.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-300\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-pen-sized-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"266\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-301\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-koozie-sized-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"266\" /> <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-307 size-full\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-cup-sized.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"266\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Standouts (Tier 2):</strong> For your $10 monthly donation, please select two (2) gifts from the following items: TF Pen, TF T-shirt, TF Koozie, TF Cup 160z.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-303\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-pen-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-304\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-shirt-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-305\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-koozie-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-308\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-cup-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Champions (Tier 3):</strong> For your $20 monthly donation, please select three (3) gifts from the following items: TF Tote, TF Mug (choose white or black), TF T-shirt, TF Cup 16oz, and any previously pictured items including TF Pen and  TF Koozie.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-309\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-tote-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-310\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-mugs-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-304\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-shirt-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-308\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-cup-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>All-Stars (Tier 4):</strong> For your $30 monthly donation, please select three (3) gifts from the following items: TF Tumbler (choose blue or black), TF Tote, TF Mug (choose white or black), TF T-shirt, and any previously pictured items including TF Cup 16oz, TF Pen and TF Koozie.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-311\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-tumblers-30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-309\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-tote-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-310\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-mugs-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-304\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-shirt-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Masters (Tier 5):</strong> For your $50 monthly donation, please select five (5) gifts from the following items: TF Polo, TF Tumbler (choose blue or black), TF Tote, TF Mug (choose white or black), and any previously pictured items including TF T-shirt, TF Cup 16oz, TF Pen and TF Koozie.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-312\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-polo-50.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-311\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-tumblers-30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-309\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-tote-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-310\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TF-mugs-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"240\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Heroes (Tier 6):</strong> For your $100 monthly donation, we will send you one of everything! And we will also provide one free entry (with guest) to a Tony Foundation event of your choice. Thank you for being a hero to families in need!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-317 size-medium aligncenter\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tickets-sized-300x129.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"129\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>What to do:</strong> Go to the Tony Foundation <a href=\"https://www.betterunite.com/tonyfoundation-makeanimpact/donate\">donation page,</a> enter the amount you wish to donate, and select \"Make this a monthly recurring payment.\" You will receive an auto-reply email asking you to specify which gifts you would like to receive.\r\n\r\nThank you for your support!!', 'Be a monthly donor and get some TF swag!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'be-a-monthly-donor-and-get-some-tf-swag', '', '', '2018-09-13 01:29:07', '2018-09-13 01:29:07', '', 0, 'http://tonyfoundation.org/?p=296', 0, 'post', '', 0),
