(319, 2, '2018-09-13 03:22:35', '2018-09-13 03:22:35', 'There can only be one. The first-ever Drive Away Cancer Golf Tournament has its first-ever Gold Sponsor: <a href=\"https://www.rebath.com/location/austin/\">Re-Bath of Austin.</a> We are honored to have their support!\n\nIt’s no surprise that such a community-oriented company like Re-Bath would step up to the tee box when it comes to helping families affected by cancer. “When they learned about our golf tournament, Re-Bath was very supportive of the cause,” said Tony Laudadio, founder of Tony Foundation. “They heard our story, and how it came about, and they asked how they could help.”\n\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-293 alignright\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rebath2-300-for-blog-300x174.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"174\" />As the Gold Sponsor, Re-Bath is helping to underwrite the Sept. 28 tournament with a $2,500 contribution. The inaugural event is already a huge success, with 128 golfers set to tee off (in teams of four) at iconic Lions Municipal Golf Course in Austin.\n\nLaudadio said that Re-Bath is a great fit for the fundraiser – and for Austin. “Everyone knows that if you hire Re-Bath, they are the company that will come in and do a great bathroom model at a great price,” Laudadio said. “In fact, I’ve had a Re-Bath remodel, and so have many of my friends, and we’ve all been very happy with the results. But did you also know how much they support this community?\n\n“They’ve always been very community oriented, they give back in so many ways, and by helping support our mission, it just demonstrates how they put that commitment into action. We’re really thrilled to have their support.”\n\n<strong>A veteran-owned-and-operated business</strong>\n\nThe Austin location is one of more than 120 Re-Bath locations in the U.S., and it was founded in 2013 by Josh and Debra Agrelius. There are currently 23 full-time employees on the Re-Bath of Austin team – each is fully licensed and insured, and Re-Bath is even a state-licensed as a plumbing company. They can help make your bathroom more stylish or more accessible for the aging or disabled, and provide a complete bathroom remodel.\n\n<strong>A special thanks to all of our sponsors</strong>\n\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-294 alignright\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Tony-Lions-blog-300x192.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"192\" />The generosity of local businesses and individuals has helped make the first Drive Away Cancer tournament a success before a single ball has been struck. “We are overwhelmed and humbled by the support we’ve received, knowing that we’ll be able to help more families thanks to contributions from all of our sponsors.\n\nWhile there are still sponsorships available, we would like to thank those who have signed up already:\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>Gold Sponsor</u></strong></h2>\n<a href=\"https://www.rebath.com/location/austin/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-340 size-full\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rebath-small-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"171\" height=\"100\" /></a>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Re-Bath of Austin</em></p>\n\n<h2></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>Hole Sponsors</u></strong></h2>\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-321 size-full\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/McCoys_Logo_2C-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"182\" height=\"90\" />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>McCoy\'s Building Supply</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.bellenviro.com/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-341 size-full\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/bell-logo-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"140\" height=\"151\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Bell Environmental, Inc.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://camden-homes.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-323\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Camden-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"120\" height=\"133\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Camden Homes</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://hominick.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-325\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/hominick-builders-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"165\" height=\"100\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Hominick Builders</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://laudadiopolymers.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-326\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/laudadio-polymers-logo-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"193\" height=\"90\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Laudadio Polymers</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://jambam.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-327\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jambam-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"190\" height=\"77\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Jambam</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://hkwhitetails.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-328\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/HnK-logo-header-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"90\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>H&amp;K Whitetails</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://christopherinv.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-329\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/CCI-logo-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"59\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Christopher Commercial</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.christianoutreachaustin.org/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-330\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/COF-logo41-300x123-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"190\" height=\"77\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Christian Outreach Foundation</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.drillchem.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-331\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/drill-chem-LLC-logo-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"184\" height=\"90\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Drillchem LLC</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://whataburger.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-335 size-full\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Whataburger-logo-small-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"140\" height=\"140\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Whataburger</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.riimgolf.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/RM-golf-Logo-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"190\" height=\"157\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>RIIM Golf Academy</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gandmplumbingtx.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-334\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/G-M-plumbing-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"140\" height=\"134\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>G&amp;M Plumbing</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://aframehs.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-336\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/AFramePNGLogo3-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"190\" height=\"80\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>A Frame Home Services</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Chuys-Logo-with-Redfish-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"151\" height=\"120\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Chuy\'s</em></p>\n<a href=\"https://scalefactor.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-338 aligncenter\" src=\"http://tonyfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ScaleFactor-Logo-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"178\" height=\"80\" /></a>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Scale Factor, Inc.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Bill and Jody Nash</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Sally Lucas</em></p>\nOur hats off to all of our sponsors for helping us make the first Drive Away Cancer Golf Tournament an amazing event to look forward to!', 'Re-Bath of Austin heads list of sponsors stepping up to the tee for Tony Foundation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '291-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-09-13 03:22:35', '2018-09-13 03:22:35', '', 291, 'http://tonyfoundation.org/291-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
